direction-type.words: Forward! be our watchword, steps and voices
Seek the things before us, not a look behind;
Burns the fiery pillar at our army's head;
Who shall dream of shrinking, by our Captain
Forward through the desert, through the toil
Jordan flows before us; Zion beams with light.
o'er yon horizon rise the city towers
the streets with jasper, shine the gates
our God abideth; that fair home
to your country, forward into light!
